Class CHCBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.chc.frontend.dsl.gen.CHCBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CHCListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class CHCBaseListener extends Object implements CHCListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CHCListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
